      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Oct 2015 16:20:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://kimpaper.github.io/en/2015/10/21/jpa-save/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In jpa you save with the repository.save method&lt;/p&gt;
